1.2.0
-----
- using scrollbarjs.add() before scrollbarjs.init() has been called doesn't do anything
- add class "scrollbarjs-active" to the element while a thumb is being dragged
- scrollbarjs.init() can only be called once
- fixed click repeat (holding mouse button) now working

